{"tid":584803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"呢球波充滿獌聯盟的 魔性 與 激情","createTime":"2018-03-08T05:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T09:01:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb15d2b7e4ab8a407bff024f20ca466d5d94deb5","tid":584803,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/sports/5aa07671e60383067d99f9bc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fsports%2F5aa07671e60383067d99f9bc%2F&d=KQPkIZW%2B%2FEF3KFCtQifZAzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4d6e08d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/sports/5aa07671e60383067d99f9bc/</a><br />\n<br />\n足球：俄超有球員趁對手受傷搶波傳中入球奠勝 引發爭拗<br />\n　2018-03-08 07:32<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯超級足球聯賽出現一個關乎體育精神的爭議入球。<br />\n<br />\n白衫艾卡馬特的艾雲洛夫，被隊友碰一碰後停下來，紅衫主隊圖拉兵工廠的甘巴洛夫偷走，球賽繼續，他傳中後，最終由哥錫打破僵局兼奠定勝局，補時險勝1-0。<br />\n<br />\n寒冷天氣冷卻不到怒火，雖然飄雪中更有英雄味道，但同時激起的火藥味更濃，觸發雙方球員推撞，當中當然包含體育精神與爭取勝利的爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n在理是沒有錯，球例沒規定。但在情，一般見有球員受傷，大多會選擇踢出界外，或放棄進攻，待球證吹停，讓對方接受治療，甘巴洛夫這次偷到3分，不過可能失盡人心，獲勝的圖拉兵工廠升上第7，比艾卡馬特高1位。"},{"pid":"1fd66bd35c940c04898ff7e9ce8182999567da5d","tid":584803,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net/photo/odai/600/052c55350ddb728981f2c3cb57a5073e_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net%2Fphoto%2Fodai%2F600%2F052c55350ddb728981f2c3cb57a5073e_600.jpg&h=d63e666a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b771c153e4457653143dc29031c1fb865bbc05d","tid":584803,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fd66bd35c940c04898ff7e9ce8182999567da5d","tid":584803,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net/photo/odai/600/052c55350ddb728981f2c3cb57a5073e_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2dcan0armyq93.cloudfro